          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " for people acting like they’re one of them. For one, such impersonators can do incredible damage to the reputation of the police. Even worse, serial killers and other offenders have used such a ploy to capture their victims.",
